<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="616" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="21.[782,1374,1171,1589]" pageId="21" pageNumber="616">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kuroda" authorityYear="1940" box="[783,986,1250,1275]" class="Mammalia" family="Talpidae" genus="Mogera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="21" pageNumber="616" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tokudae">Mogera tokudae</taxonomicName>
occurs on Sado Island, and this restricted distribution is suggested to have formed during the Quaternary histo- ry of the Japanese mole fauna. 
<taxonomicName box="[1216,1374,1364,1393]" class="Mammalia" family="Talpidae" genus="Mogera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="21" pageNumber="616" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="etigo">Mogera etigo</taxonomicName>
is the oldest lineage of Japanese moles, and its distribution might have been displaced by the younger lineages of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kuroda" baseAuthorityYear="1957" class="Mammalia" family="Talpidae" genus="Mogera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="21" pageNumber="615" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="imaizumii">M. imaizumii</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Temminck" authorityYear="1842" box="[925,1066,1521,1550]" class="Mammalia" family="Talpidae" genus="Talpa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="21" pageNumber="615" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="wogura">M. wogura</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[782,1181,1556,1589]" pageId="21" pageNumber="616" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6678215" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6678215" box="[782,1181,1556,1589]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6678215/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="616" targetBox="[167,758,1171,1576]" targetPageId="21">
<paragraph blockId="21.[782,1374,1171,1589]" box="[782,1181,1556,1589]" pageId="21" pageNumber="616">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[782,957,1556,1589]" pageId="21" pageNumber="616">Distribution.</emphasis>
